summary: Through both my education and my home background I have been immersed in an international environment. I have learned to work efficiently under pressure, to adapt quickly to new environments and deal with people from different cultures. I consider myself a hard working person who strives for excellence in whatever I do: work, study and sports. My self-motivation transfers onto other people making me capable of being a team leader and team player.
